Package: robustOffset
Type: Package
Title: Robust normalization of gene expression data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: K.K.M. Koudijs
Maintainer: K.K.M. Koudijs <k.k.m.koudijs@lumc.nl>
Description: Condense a panel of reference genes into a single sample offset, which captures systematic systematic changes in gene expression. See https://github.com/kkmkoudijs/robustOffsets for tutorial on how to use. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
  lme4,
  reshape2
